metadata.name: 00:16 Lost in Space
metadata.description:
“Mayday Mayday! Something happened at 00:16 while a group of the Moon Invaders was heading to the moon. The Spaceship suddenly disappeared. We have lost contact with them. We don’t know where they are and there is no sign of life…”

  Characters and animation by @Pepperon1st
Spaceship and Scene Design by @Vasato
Music: “Nova” by 2050 


Kind: MP4
Duration: 34 seconds
Dimension: 2880x2000
